ipts_written','2026-04-02',NULL,'script 1',812,'text','script 1 \nGirl (suspicious):\nHello itni raat ko call? Girlfriend so gayi kya?\n\nBoy (confused):\nKya? Meri koi girlfriend hi nahi hai!\n\nGirl (teasing):\nHaan haan… sab yahi bolte hain.\n\nBoy (dramatic):\nSach mein yaar… meri life mein sirf problems hain.\n\nGirl (laughing):\nAchha? Toh main kya hoon?\n\nBoy (quick, funny):\nTum premium problem ho\nGirl (playful):\nAchha hua HiMa pe mile… warna tumhari life boring hi rehti.\n\nBoy (laughing):\nSach mein… yahan problems bhi premium milti hain\n\nscript 2 \nBoy:\n Tumne call kyun kiya achanak?\nGirl:\n Bas yaad aa rahe the tum.\nBoy:\n Acha? Itni jaldi miss karne lagi?\nGirl:\n Haan thoda zyada hi.\nBoy:\n Dangerous ho tum.\nGirl:\n Toh sambhal lo warna aur aadat ho jaungi.\n\nBoy:\nWaise… hum mile bhi toh HiMa pe hi the na.\n\nGirl:\nHaan… aur dekho, strangers se kitni achi story ban gayi',21,'2026-04-02 11:22:33','2026-04-02 11:22:33'),(83,21,'ai_videos_generated','2026-04-02','creative_uploads/2026-04-02/Ve0aLfOFEmR7ZepopLSSlm34FZHqp5FRmIt8LiMR.mp4','WhatsApp Video 2026-04-02 at 4.17.55 PM.mp4',4488392,'mp4',NULL,21,'2026-04-02 11:23:40','2026-04-02 11:23:40'),(84,21,'ai_videos_generated','2026-04-02','creative_uploads/2026-04-02/CFKs9v3F1uqwi1jTx1rOJlbfcsmLzWFuFsIkmTAA.mp4','WhatsApp Video 2026-04-02 at 4.55.02 PM.mp4',5690935,'mp4',NULL,21,'2026-04-02 11:25:43','2026-04-02 11:25:43'),(85,22,'ai_videos_generated','2026-04-02','creative_uploads/2026-04-02/S04u5GC328YCuHAtpYMUEHcKpog4gxAPZQhIrIUB.mp4','0402 (1).mp4',34900723,'mp4',NULL,22,'2026-04-02 11:51:16','2026-04-02 11:51:16'),(86,22,'ai_videos_generated','2026-04-02','creative_uploads/2026-04-02/sQQS2VoLuAF0IWcibZPnyGmH877sUjk6qtkTYqQp.mp4','0402.mp4',39289370,'mp4',NULL,22,'2026-04-02 11:51:22','2026-04-02 11:51:22'),(87,40,'ad_scripts_written','2026-04-02',NULL,'Female- iroju ela nenu gurthu vachanu meku',317,'text','Female- iroju ela nenu gurthu vachanu meku \nMale- ala emi ledu meru eppudu na all