g Claude for content and image generation [4:24]. * @Krishnan Krishnan will create a Google sheet for tracking daily content creation [6:32]. * Await meta dashboard from Ruth, expected by next week [9:53].','',2,1223,'2026-03-27 07:35:37','2026-03-27 07:35:37'),(1771,'tech-lead-hima-standup-fri','2026-03-23','What tasks were completed yesterday?','@Rishabh Kumar confirmed completing his side of work and preparing for testing',1,1231,'2026-03-27 14:17:13','2026-03-30 02:22:57'),(1772,'tech-lead-hima-standup-fri','2026-03-23','What tasks were completed yesterday?','@Sivaperumal\'s code was prepared for merging',1,1232,'2026-03-27 14:17:13','2026-03-30 02:22:57'),(1773,'tech-lead-hima-standup-fri','2026-03-23','What tasks were completed yesterday?','Not discussed',1,1233,'2026-03-27 14:17:13','2026-03-30 02:22:57'),(1774,'tech-lead-hima-standup-fri','2026-03-23','What are you working on today?','Preparing for APK testing and troubleshooting Ludo app connectivity',1,1234,'2026-03-27 14:17:13','2026-03-30 02:22:57'),(1775,'tech-lead-hima-standup-fri','2026-03-23','What are you working on today?','Planning next sprint and resolving current sprint tasks',1,1236,'2026-03-27 14:17:13','2026-03-30 02:22:57'),(1776,'tech-lead-hima-standup-fri','2026-03-23','What are you working on today?','Not discussed',1,1235,'2026-03-27 14:17:13','2026-03-30 02:22:57'),(1777,'tech-lead-hima-standup-fri','2026-03-23','Any bugs fixed or reported yesterday?','Audio call connectivity problems reported by @Raksha Agarwal',1,1237,'2026-03-27 14:17:13','2026-03-30 02:22:57'),(1778,'tech-lead-hima-standup-fri','2026-03-23','Any bugs fixed or reported yesterday?','Not discussed',1,1238,'2026-03-27 14:17:13','2026-03-30 02:22:57'),(1779,'tech-lead-hima-standup-fri','2026-03-23','Any bugs fixed or reported yesterday?','Not discussed',1,1239,'2026-03-27 14:17:13','2026-03-30 02:22:57'),(1780,'tech-lead-hima-standup-fri','2026-03-23','Any open bugs that need attention?','Audio call connectivity issues i