:00].\n    * The team discussed potential solutions for default OTP implementation and alternative authentication methods [30:57].\n\n\n* Server Deployment Configuration\n    * @Yuvanesh noted that server deployment requires manual addition of API keys and environment variables [15:50].\n    * @Rishabh Kumar requested specific environment variable details to ensure proper backend functionality [12:58].\n    * The team collaborated to identify and set the correct credentials for live deployment [20:55].\n* User Registration Workflow\n    * @Yuvanesh suggested exploring alternative authentication methods similar to Uber\'s sign-in process [30:45].\n    * The team discussed potential user registration flow, including whether to collect user details on the same page or redirect to a separate page',35,'2026-03-25 13:17:35','2026-03-25 13:17:35'),(107,'qa-daily-standup-raksha-laxmi-wed','2026-03-23','Worked on testing the Ludo feature in the Hi Ma app, ensuring smooth gameplay during calls without affecting audio/video functionality.',36,'2026-03-25 18:17:33','2026-03-25 18:17:33'),(108,'cfo-stand-up-meeting-thu','2026-03-23','1. Mails to Vendors,\n2. Sales Report to Sangeetaha,\n3. Final PAN List to Ayush\n4. Vendors Reco\n5. Speak with CS Ruchi &  Ambika on Payroll - Labour Law Compliances - PF, ESIC, PTEC & PTRC - Mandatory + Gratuity Fund + Super Annuation Fund etc., creation\n6. Speak with Tanbir - Phonepe\n7. Speak with Chaithra - TDS Notice\n8. Accounting - March 2026 3rd Week\n9. Invoices - Request to all the cheifs and Tech head\n10. Correct Entries of previous months and finalise. 11. TDS Reco & GST Reco - Must. We do not have much time left. Remaining Pending - 4, 5, 6, 7, 10, 11',32,'2026-03-26 05:02:20','2026-03-26 05:02:20'),(109,'marketing-standup-daily-thu','2026-03-23','Today Leave',3,'2026-03-26 05:42:16','2026-03-26 05:42:16'),(110,'ops-standup-daily-thu','2026-03-23','Summary\n\n* Ticket Resolution Performance\n    * @Ranjini completed 95 total tickets