INSERT INTO `tessa_messages` VALUES (1,59,'user','Sign in for today','2026-03-16 02:41:26'),(2,59,'assistant','Good morning, Yuvanesh! ☀️ Happy Monday — let\'s get you set up for the week ahead.\n\n## Morning Briefing for Monday, March 16, 2026\n\n| Section | Details | Status |\n|---|---|---|\n| **Meeting 1** | Hima Tech Standup @ 10:30 AM — Owner — Attendees: Rishabh, Raksha | Agenda: Partial, Notes: Empty |\n| **Meeting 2** | Only Care Standup Tech @ 11:00 AM — Owner — Attendees: Maari | Agenda: Empty, Notes: Empty |\n| **Meeting 3** | Sudar + Thedal Standup Tech @ 12:00 PM — Owner — Attendees: Tamil Arasan, Perumal | Agenda: Partial, Notes: Empty |\n| **Meeting 4** | QA Daily Standup @ 2:30 PM — Attendee — Attendees: Raksha, Laxmi | — |\n| **Daily Reports (Sun)** | Yuvanesh: n/a, Rishabh: n/a, Perumal: n/a, Maari: n/a (Sunday) | N/A |\n| **Daily Reports (Sun)** | Raksha (QA Analyst) — missing report | ⚠️ Missing |\n| **Dashboard** | 0/5 team members clear — all pending (Maari, Perumal, Raksha, Rishabh, Yuvanesh) | Pending |\n\n### 🔔 Quick Heads-Up\n- **Agendas need attention** — Only Care Standup Tech has an empty agenda, and two others are only partial. Worth filling those in before your meetings kick off.\n- **Raksha\'s Sunday report** is missing — you may want to follow up with her before the Hima standup at 10:30.\n- You own **3 back-to-back meetings** from 10:30 AM to 12:00 PM — plan some prep time before 10:30.\n\nYou\'ve got a busy morning ahead. How can I help — want to start prepping agendas or draft a reminder to Raksha?','2026-03-16 02:41:40'),(3,59,'user','how to do kpi','2026-03-16 03:02:55'),(4,59,'assistant','Great question! Here\'s a quick overview of how KPIs work in the system:\n\n### What are KPIs?\n\nKPIs (Key Performance Indicators) are measurable targets tracked for your team — things like sprint velocity, bug resolution time, deployment frequency, etc.\n\n---\n\nHowever, I don\'t have specific details on:\n- What KPIs are currently configured for your team\n- How to set them up or update them in the platform\n- What thresholds or targets are in place\n\nThis is something that would depend on how your admin or project setup has configured KPIs within the InnovFix/Hima platform.\n\n### What I\'d suggest:\n1. **Check with your platform admin** — they can walk you through where KPIs are configured\n2. **Look in your dashboard settings** — there may be a KPI section under team or project settings\n3. **Let me know what you want to track** — I can help you define meaningful KPIs for your team (e.g., sprint completion rate, PR turnaround time, bug count per release, etc.)\n\nWant me to help you brainstorm relevant KPIs for your engineering team? 🎯','2026-03-16 03:03:11'),(5,60,'user','Show my pending work','2026-03-16 03:13:30'),(6,60,'assistant','## Pending Work for Monday, Mar 16\n\nHere\'s everything that needs your attention today:\n\n| Item | Details | Status |\n|------|---------|--------|\n| **Daily Report** | Yesterday\'s report (Sunday, Mar 15) is missing | ⚠️ Missing |\n| **Meeting Prep** | Thedal - Daily Standup @ 12:00 PM — You\'re the owner. Agenda is partial, notes are empty. | ⚠️ Needs Attention |\n| **KPIs** | Week of Mar 9 — 0/6 targets entered | ⚠️ Incomplete |\n\n### Quick Summary\n- **3 items** need your attention before the day wraps up.\n- **Priority suggestion:** Start with yesterday\'s daily report, then finalize the agenda for the 12:00 PM standup with Bala, and update your KPI entries when you get a chance.\n\nLet me know if you\'d like help drafting any of these!','2026-03-16 03:13:40'),(7,60,'user','Sign in for today','2026-03-16 03:13:59'),(8,60,'assistant','Good morning, Dhanush! ☀️ Happy Monday — let\'s get the week started strong!\n\n## Morning Briefing for Monday, Mar 16, 2026\n\n| Section | Details | Status |\n|---------|---------|--------|\n| **Today\'s Meetings** | Thedal - Daily Standup @ 12:00 PM — Owner: You, Attendee: Bala | ⚠️ Agenda partial, Notes empty |\n| **Pending