 | Details | Status |\n|------|---------|--------|\n| Daily Report (Yesterday - Wed, Mar 25) | Not submitted | ❌ Missing |\n| Daily Report (Today - Thu, Mar 26) | Not submitted | ❌ Missing |\n\nHere\'s what you can do:\n\n### Troubleshooting Steps\n\n1. **Check your access** — Make sure you\'re logged into the correct InnovFix/Hima account and have the right permissions.\n2. **Try a different browser** — Sometimes cache or extension issues can block form submissions. Try incognito mode or a different browser.\n3. **Clear cache & cookies** — If the page isn\'t loading properly, clearing your browser data may help.\n4. **Check your internet connection** — A weak connection can cause submission failures.\n\n### If the issue persists\n\n- **Reach out to your team lead or manager** and let them know you\'re facing a technical issue so they\'re aware of the delay.\n- **Contact IT support** — They can check if there\'s a platform issue or a permissions problem on your account.\n\nIn the meantime, I\'d recommend documenting what you\'d put in your daily report (tasks completed, blockers, plans) so you can submit it quickly once the issue is resolved.\n\nIs there a specific error message you\'re seeing? That might help narrow down the problem.','2026-03-26 13:17:46'),(1538,69,'user','Give me hima link','2026-03-26 13:18:02'),(1539,69,'assistant','I\'m sorry, Shoyab — I don\'t have the direct link to the Hima platform in my available data.\n\n### What you can try:\n\n1. **Check your email** — Look for any onboarding or welcome emails from Hima/InnovFix that may contain the platform URL.\n2. **Check your bookmarks** — You may have saved it previously.\n3. **Ask your team lead or IT support** — They can share the correct link quickly.\n4. **Check Slack** — The link may have been shared in a team channel or pinned message.\n\nWould you like me to **send a Slack DM** to someone on your team to get the link for you? Let me know! 🙂','2026-03-26 13:18:19'),(1540,69,'user','Contacted