as the issue is fixed.\n3. **Once submitted**, come back and say **\"sign me off\"** — I\'ll get you signed off right away.\n\nIf the issue isn\'t resolved today, I\'d recommend **informing your manager** about the technical blocker so the delay is documented.\n\nIs there anything else I can help with while you wait? 🙂','2026-03-26 13:20:06'),(1547,69,'assistant','I appreciate you sharing that, Shoyab, but unfortunately **I can\'t submit your daily report on your behalf**. The report needs to be submitted directly on the **Hima platform**.\n\nHowever, you\'ve got your content ready — that\'s great! Here\'s what you shared:\n\n> 1. Follow-up with vendors including Cashfree, Phonepe, etc.\n> 2. Coordinating with CFO Angle for TDS Notice\n> 3. Accounting in Tally - for March 2026 - 3rd Week in WIP\n\n### Next Steps:\n\n- Since you\'ve already **contacted your team** about the platform issue, wait for their response to get access.\n- Once you\'re in, **copy-paste the above** into your daily report fields and submit.\n- Then come back and say **\"sign me off\"** — I\'ll be here! 🙂\n\nIs there anything else I can help with in the meantime?','2026-03-26 13:20:11'),(1548,71,'user','Sign off for today','2026-03-26 14:12:19'),(1549,71,'assistant','## Sign-Off Checklist — Thursday, March 26, 2026\n\n| Item | Status |\n|------|--------|\n| **Daily Report (Yesterday, Mar 25)** | ⚠️ Not submitted |\n| **Pending Action Items** | ✅ Complete (0 pending) |\n\nLooks like your **daily report for yesterday (Wednesday, Mar 25)** is still pending. I\'d recommend submitting that before signing off.\n\nOnce that\'s done, come back and we\'ll get you signed off! 💪','2026-03-26 14:12:30'),(1550,71,'user','Sign in for today','2026-03-26 14:12:59'),(1551,71,'user','Sign off for today','2026-03-26 14:13:00'),(1552,71,'assistant','Good morning, Barkha! ☀️ Happy Thursday — here\'s your day at a glance!\n\n## Morning Briefing for Thursday, March 26, 2026\n\n| Section | Details | Status |\n|--------